# Submit an encoding task

Initialize ApsaraVideo Media Processing \(MPS\) in the MPS console according to the instructions in Activate MPS. To submit an encoding task, follow these steps:

1.  Log on to the [MPS console](https://mps.console.aliyun.com).
2.  Log on to the [MPS console](https://partners-intl.aliyun.com/login-required#/mps).
3.  Select a region.
4.  In the left-side navigation pane, click **Tasks**.
5.  On the Encode tab, click **Create Task**.
6.  Set basic parameters, including Input File URL, Encoding Pipeline, Output File Name, and Output Path. Then, click **Next**.![](https://static-aliyun-doc.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/assets/img/en-US/1391421951/p9963.png)
7.  Set output parameters, including Template Type, Output Format, and Template. Then, click **Submit**.

    ![](https://static-aliyun-doc.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/assets/img/en-US/1391421951/p9964.png)

8.  View the encoding status and result.

    On the **Encode** tab of the **Tasks** page, specify the time range and pipeline. Then, click **Search** to view encoding tasks that meet the specified conditions.********

    -   **View encoding tasks and encoding statuses.**

        ![](https://static-aliyun-doc.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/assets/img/en-US/1391421951/p9965.png)

    -   Click the encoding ID of a task or click **Details** in the Actions column of the task to view details of the task.********![](https://static-aliyun-doc.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/assets/img/en-US/2391421951/p9966.png)

